Interface IgnoreAnalyzerBridge

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BigDecimalBridge, BigIntegerBridge, BooleanBridge, ByteBridge, DoubleBridge, FloatBridge, IntegerBridge, LongBridge, NumberBridge, NumericEncodingCalendarBridge, NumericEncodingDateBridge, NumericFieldBridge, ShortBridge, StringEncodingCalendarBridge, StringEncodingDateBridge, UriBridge, UrlBridge, UUIDBridge

    public interface IgnoreAnalyzerBridge
    This interface is used to mark the bridges we want to keep safe from the analyzers.
    Author:
    Guillaume Smet
    Experimental
    This contract is currently under active development and may be altered in future releases, breaking existing users.
